Title: Fix "Reset Counter" option in distributed setups
Level: 1
Component: ec
Compatible: incomp
Edition: cre
Version: 1.6.0p25
Date: 1620034589
Class: fix

If you used the option "Reset Counter" in distributed setups, only the rule
counters for the local event console were reseted.

If you used this option before, please check if you have to reset counters for
all sites again.
